<bibRefCitation id="7F0158DBCE3902026E88FA27627435BE" author="GORY, H. L." box="[988,1108,1432,1456]" pageId="3" pageNumber="84" pagination="43 - 52" refId="ref15017" refString="GORY, H. L. 1841. Histoire naturelle et iconographie des insectes Coleopteres. Supplement aux Buprestides. Paris, P. Dumenil. Volume 4, livraisons 43 - 52, genera: Melanophila pp. 73 - 77; Buprestis p. 107 - 111,126; p. 127 - 356, Stigmodera, Colobogaster, Chrysobothris, Belionota, Castalia, Poecilonota, Zemina, Stenogaster, Agrilus, Amorphosoma, Eumerus, Coraebus, Anthaxia, Evagora, Sphenoptera, Sponsor, Brachys, Trachys, Aphanisticus." type="journal article" year="1841">Gory, 1841</bibRefCitation>
